title: 2016 Week 4 Review
itunes:title: 2016 Week 4 Review
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, and Marc Sessler – go game-by-game recapping all of Sunday’s action including rookies Dak Prescott and Ezekiel Elliot carrying the Cowboys to a come-from-behind win over the 49ers, and two of last year’s powerhouse teams falling to 1-3 on the season.
